// Steps to deploy an app on Heroku

//url to see your projects on heroku dashboard -  https://dashboard.heroku.com/

1. Fisrt download Heroku CLI
2. login into the Heroku CLI - heroku login -> Using this command you will be redirect to login page of heroku CLI
3. you need to create heroku app
   -> heroku create <Name of app>
   you will get two links
   1. link-of-app : https://chat-room-vp.herokuapp.com/
   2. git : https://git.heroku.com/chat-room-vp.git
4. Now we need to push our code to above git repository,
    for that run command -> git push heroku master